### Reset Password API Test Cases
### POST /api/auth/reset-password
### 
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code
### 
### Instructions:
### 1. First, call forgot-password API to get a reset token
### 2. Check server logs (development) or email for the token
### 3. Replace the token value below
### 4. Click "Send Request"

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@contentType = application/json

### ✅ Test 1: Valid Reset Token
### Note: Replace with actual reset token from forgot-password
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "token": "REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_RESET_TOKEN",
  "password": "NewSecurePass123!"
}

